---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Command OS">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Command OS</p>
      <h1>A repeatable system for reading SaaS launch work.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Codex Workplace organizes the path from campaign work to funnel movement, content decisions,
        launch checks, and production deployment.
      </p>
      <div class="grid gateway-grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>1. Brief</h3><p>Capture the offer, target visitor, work channel, and conversion hypothesis.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>2. Route</h3><p>Map campaigns, pages, and follow-up paths before spend starts to scatter.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>3. Generate</h3><p>Create brand visuals, launch media, and content assets through fal.ai.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>4. Observe</h3><p>Review work quality, content signal, and funnel movement in one surface.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>5. Deploy</h3><p>Keep Cloudflare, Railway, DNS, and release checks tied to the same launch record.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>6. Iterate</h3><p>Turn each launch pass into the next copy, content, or campaign decision.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gateway-grid {
    margin-top: 42px;
  }
</style>
